    A list of contacts that enforces uniqueness between its elements and does not allow nulls. A contact is considered unique by comparing using Person#isSamePerson(Person). As such, adding and updating of contacts uses Person#isSamePerson(Person) for equality so as to ensure that the contact being added or updated is unique in terms of identity in the UniquePersonList. However, the removal of a contact uses Person#equals(Object) so as to ensure that the contact with exactly the same fields will be removed. Supports a minimal set of list operations.
